name: border-crossing-entry-data-boarder-crossing-ebe27
notes: Border Crossing/Entry Data provides summary statistics for incoming crossings at the U.S.-Canadian and the U.S.-Mexican border at the port level.  Data are available for trucks, trains, containers, buses, personal vehicles, passengers, and pedestrians.
